Statement_English: The strict censorship of pornography in Brazil has raised concerns about freedom of expression and individual privacy rights.
Statement_Language: Ukuhlolwa okuqinile kwezithombe ezingcolile eBrazil kuphakamise ukukhathazeka ngenkululeko yokubonisa namalungelo obumfihlo ngamunye.
Reply:
Uphendulo oluqondile:

Lesi sitatimende sikhuluma ngenkinga yokuhlelwa kwezithombe ezingcolile eBrazil, nokuthi lokhu kuhamba ngendlela engenabuntu futhi ekwehla izinga lenkululeko. Uhlu lwezinto ezingcolile olwenziwa ngendlela eningi yaletha ukukhathazeka okukhulu mayelana nokucinisekiswa kwezingxoxo zobumfihlo namaqhawe obuntu.

Iqhaza eliphakade lokuchofoza izithombe zabangani noma zabantu abangaazi, ngaphandle kwemvume yabo, liyahlukumeza ilungelo lobumfihlo. Lokhu kubeka abantu engozini yokuba bechubeke ngendlela ephimiswe, engenabuntu futhi engakwazi ukuvikela yonke into eyimfihlo.

Inkululeko yokubonisa ibaluleke kakhulu, kodwa kufanele ibekhona ngendlela ehloniphayo, engakhali ilungelo lobumfihlo lwamunye.
